{"tid":835183,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個家姐惡頂既地方","createTime":"2018-09-24T16:26:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-26T00:03:46.000Z","uid":118642,"like":16,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"a2000f07b2c5f012410780b1f42bc2a2eef01b4f","tid":835183,"uid":118642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T16:26:09.000Z","msg":"條友真係好煩<br />\n次次返到黎啲家務一樣都唔做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己食完啲野又唔洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n叫佢洗又話返完工好攰唔想做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大佬呀全世界人都係咁架啦<br />\n個個都有自己既工作<br />\n成日將自己啲工作掉俾人做<br />\n衫又唔洗放成個星期都唔洗<br />\n之前試過成5日冇返去<br />\n返到去啲衫勁臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最on9係人地洗少一次碗就即刻打俾老母督你背脊<br />\n屋企好亂呀媽咪你返黎做家務啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好心反省下自己點解就黎30歲都嫁唔出啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n未聽過有男仔岳母俾埋首期都唔想娶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有咩方法可以對付呢啲港女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"752e24da364c2e381fddcd2f25a78778cdc300ec","tid":835183,"uid":118642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T16:26:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a3c0d1f0ccf09b18f3b630b53f1d17925272b6f","tid":835183,"uid":60113,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T16:28:05.000Z","msg":"俾我奶佢個閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84cd754328ca7ecc8354c7ced2b78d9121084a3e","tid":835183,"uid":118642,"like":0,"dislike"